title: Colts-Titans TNF Recap: There's a new leader in the AFC South (Football 11/13)
description:
Will Brinson is happy because NC State alum performed well. John Breech is happy because special teams were a major storyline in this game. Ryan Wilson is happy because we kept this episode under 30 minutes. So join the Pick Six Superfriends as they recap the Colts 34-17 victory over the Titans on Thursday Night Football. The guys break down the new AFC South hierarchy, delve into an analytics discussion, assess where Ryan Tannehill falls among the league's best QBs and closely dissect special teams woes for Tennessee.
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
